n_reversion, etc.)\\n  confidence: number,      // Signal confidence (0-1)\\n  d
irection: string,       // \'YES\' or \'NO\'\\n  contracts: number,       // Num
ber of contracts\\n  entry_price: number,     // Entry price in cents\\n  exit_p
rice: number,      // Exit price (when closed)\\n  status: string,          // \
