DING\'\\n  created_at: string,      // Creation timestamp\\n  updated_at: string
,      // Last update timestamp\\n  metadata: object         // Additional trade
data\\n}\\n```\\n\\n**Storage location:** `output/paper_trades.db`\\n\\n**API Me
thods:**\\n- `recordTrade(trade)` - Record a new paper trade\\n- `updateTrade(id
