eer)  \\n**Date:** 2026-04-03  \\n**Status:** ✅ Complete\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Objec
tive\\n\\nValidate that the T326 fetchCandles() fix produces meaningful paper tr
ade metrics by running 50+ trades with deterministic data.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Meth
odology\\n\\n### Batch Paper Trading Script\\n\\nCreated `backend/scripts/batch_
paper_trade.js` to:\\n1. Clear existing paper trade database\\n2. Run `live_runn
er.js --execute` multiple times\\n3. Collect trades until target reached\\n4. Ge
nerate summary statistics\\n\\n### Execution\\n\\n```bash\\n$ node backend/scrip
ts/batch_paper_trade.js\\n\\n=== Batch Paper Trading Validation (Task 327) ===\\
n\\nTarget: 50+ trades\\nRuns planned: 20\\n\\nRun 1/20... ✓ 3 signals | Total t
rades: 3\\nRun 2/20... ✓ 3 signals | Total trades: 6\\n...\\nRun 17/20... ✓ 3 si
gnals | Total trades: 51\\n\\n🎯 Target reached! 51 trades generated.\\n```\\n\\
n---\\n\\n## Results\\n\\n### Trade Statistics\\n\\n| Metric | Value |\\n|------
--|-------|\\n| **Total Trades** | 51 |\\n| **Target Reached** | ✅ 51/50 |\\n| 
**Runs Executed** | 17 |\\n| **Avg Signals/Run** | 3.0 |\\n| **Open Trades** | 5
