-20260501-T150000 | 17 | YES | 95% |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## API Endpoint: GET /api/pnl
/live\\n\\nNew endpoint provides real-time paper trading metrics:\\n\\n```json\\
n{\\n  \\"success\\": true,\\n  \\"timestamp\\": \\"2026-04-03T19:09:29.601Z\\",
