es\\": 0,\\n  \\"last_10_trades\\": [...],\\n  \\"by_strategy\\": {},\\n  \\"las
t_updated\\": \\"2026-04-03T19:09:10.031Z\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### Endpoint Details
