trades win rate (0-1) |\\n| `total_pnl` | Realized P&L in dollars |\\n| `trade_c
ount` | Total trades (open + closed) |\\n| `closed_trades` | Trades with settled
outcomes |\\n| `open_trades` | Trades awaiting settlement |\\n| `last_10_trades`
| Most recent trades with details |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Observations\\n\\n### ✅ Po
sitive Findings\\n\\n1. **Deterministic data working**: Same 3 markets generated
consistently across runs\\n2. **Signal generation stable**: Exactly 3 signals pe
r run (mean_reversion only)\\n3. **High confidence**: All signals at 95% confide
nce (above 0.80 threshold)\\n4. **Risk checks passing**: All trades approved by 
