trades = no win rate or P&L yet\\n2. **Need market settlement**: Requires actual
market outcomes to calculate P&L\\n3. **3 markets only**: Limited diversity in f
allback market data\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Next Steps for Full Validation\\n\\nTo meas
ure win rate convergence toward 55.9% backtest baseline:\\n\\n1. **Trade Resolut
ion**: Implement automatic trade closing when markets settle\\n2. **Historical S
ettlement**: Load historical market outcomes for back-testing\\n3. **Extended Ru
